He'll shadowbox all the way home.

1232
00:45:04,902 --> 00:45:07,238
He'll be fine.
He'll shadowbox all the way home.

1233
00:45:07,605 --> 00:45:08,973
Wait, this isn't right.

1234
00:45:09,774 --> 00:45:11,742
Who shadowboxes when they're sleeping?

1235
00:45:11,809 --> 00:45:14,045
- I do that.
- Oh, do you?

1236
00:45:14,111 --> 00:45:15,713
- Do you really?
- Sometimes I do this in bed.

1237
00:45:15,780 --> 00:45:16,981
- For real?
- Come on.

1238
00:45:17,048 --> 00:45:19,283
Do you do that when you're
going to the bathroom at night?

1239
00:45:19,350 --> 00:45:20,484
Yes, I do it like this.

1240
00:45:21,752 --> 00:45:22,820
Hold on.

1241
00:45:25,556 --> 00:45:27,325
Then how do you flush the toilet?

1242
00:45:27,391 --> 00:45:29,060
This is how I do it.

1243
00:45:29,227 --> 00:45:30,661
This is how I do it.

1244
00:45:32,196 --> 00:45:34,565
That's incredible.

1245
00:45:34,632 --> 00:45:36,701
She looks so done with you.

1246
00:45:36,767 --> 00:45:38,536
She's done with you.

1247
00:45:41,205 --> 00:45:43,074
Sorry, Min-young.

1248
00:45:46,043 --> 00:45:47,945
<i>They're so silly.</i>

1249
00:45:48,813 --> 00:45:52,116
<i>Their chats today drowned out</i>
<i>the sound of frying chicken.</i>

1250
00:45:52,450 --> 00:45:54,418
<i>But anyway, that's it for today.</i>

1251
00:45:54,485 --> 00:45:56,354
<i>We were the chaotic Chicken Sisters!</i>

1252
00:45:57,321 --> 00:45:59,257
Stop it now!

1253
00:45:59,423 --> 00:46:02,159
How was it today?
Time flies when you're having fun, right?

1254
00:46:02,226 --> 00:46:05,029
It was so chaotic and hilarious.

1255
00:46:05,096 --> 00:46:06,764
- It was fun, right?
- Definitely.

1256
00:46:06,831 --> 00:46:08,199
I had a great time.

1257
00:46:09,100 --> 00:46:10,835
So the Cops and Robbers club--

1258
00:46:10,901 --> 00:46:13,504
Sorry about that. I need to get this.

1259
00:46:14,939 --> 00:46:15,906
Hello?

1260
00:46:16,274 --> 00:46:19,176
Hi, Jung-woo! What's up?

1261
00:46:19,243 --> 00:46:21,979
<i>Legwork Club is meeting next week, right?</i>

1262
00:46:22,046 --> 00:46:24,448
Oh, do you finally have
some free time now?

1263
00:46:24,682 --> 00:46:25,916
Yes, we'll see you then.

1264
00:46:25,983 --> 00:46:28,052
We just got kicked out of a club,
so we have time.

1265
00:46:28,119 --> 00:46:30,221
- Yes, tell him to come.
- All right.

1266
00:46:30,288 --> 00:46:31,622
- You two, get out.
- Yes.

1267
00:46:31,689 --> 00:46:32,657
- Go.
- You should leave.

1268
00:46:32,723 --> 00:46:33,658
- Go away.
- Okay.

1269
00:46:33,724 --> 00:46:34,759
- Let's go.
- Yes, go away.

1270
00:46:34,825 --> 00:46:35,726
Worst of luck to your club.

1271
00:46:35,793 --> 00:46:37,094
I hope your club falls apart.

1272
00:46:37,161 --> 00:46:38,195
Bye now.

1273
00:46:51,642 --> 00:46:53,177
- Delivery is so tiring.
- You scared me.

1274
00:46:54,345 --> 00:46:56,647
Don't go around wearing a ski mask!

1275
00:46:56,714 --> 00:46:58,349
- Why not?
- This is why

1276
00:46:58,416 --> 00:47:00,351
our customers are too scared to come here!

1277
00:47:00,418 --> 00:47:03,154
I played a round of Cops and Robbers
during delivery.

1278
00:47:03,220 --> 00:47:05,856
It was so exhilarating and funny.

1279
00:47:05,923 --> 00:47:07,858
Some guy was chasing me,

1280
00:47:07,925 --> 00:47:09,627
and only me!

1281
00:47:09,694 --> 00:47:10,861
It was so exciting.

1282
00:47:10,928 --> 00:47:12,396
What if he's into me?

1283
00:47:14,665 --> 00:47:16,600
Don't be ridiculous!

1284
00:47:17,101 --> 00:47:18,602
Wait a minute.

1285
00:47:20,171 --> 00:47:21,305
What are you doing?

1286
00:47:23,341 --> 00:47:25,943
You actually ordered fried chicken
from some other restaurant?

1287
00:47:26,010 --> 00:47:27,845
Are you out of your mind?

1288
00:47:27,912 --> 00:47:30,448
See, this is where you and I differ.

1289
00:47:30,715 --> 00:47:33,050
This is the most popular fried chicken
in the neighborhood,

1290
00:47:33,117 --> 00:47:35,486
so obviously I had to do market research.

1291
00:47:35,553 --> 00:47:37,822
This is the reason
our business isn't booming.

1292
00:47:37,888 --> 00:47:40,057
Come on. Are you serious?

1293
00:47:40,124 --> 00:47:41,559
- Try it and see for yourself.
- You're unbelievable.

1294
00:47:41,625 --> 00:47:43,427
You have to know your enemy, right?

1295
00:47:43,494 --> 00:47:45,129
What kind of insane tactic is this?

1296
00:47:45,196 --> 00:47:48,499
We need to study this
to make our chicken better.

1297
00:47:51,669 --> 00:47:52,636
No way.

1298
00:47:53,170 --> 00:47:55,406
It's so good.

1299
00:47:57,475 --> 00:47:59,877
It's so crisp on the outside

1300
00:48:00,644 --> 00:48:01,712
and so...

1301
00:48:02,313 --> 00:48:04,782
juicy and chewy on the inside.

1302
00:48:04,849 --> 00:48:06,117
- What the heck?
- See?

1303
00:48:06,183 --> 00:48:07,885
It's because they fried it whole.

1304
00:48:07,952 --> 00:48:11,188
That's why the meat is so juicy.

1305
00:48:11,355 --> 00:48:13,190
This is their secret.

1306
00:48:13,457 --> 00:48:16,127
- You see how crisp it is on the outside?
- Yes.

1307
00:48:16,193 --> 00:48:17,661
But it's still soft on the inside.

1308
00:48:17,928 --> 00:48:20,197
It's all the rage these days.

1309
00:48:20,264 --> 00:48:22,533
You'd think it wouldn't make
much of a difference

1310
00:48:22,600 --> 00:48:24,268
whether it's cooked whole or not,

1311
00:48:24,502 --> 00:48:25,803
but it really does.

1312
00:48:25,870 --> 00:48:27,471
It's so juicy.

1313
00:48:30,307 --> 00:48:32,143
- Welcome.
- Hello.

1314
00:48:32,209 --> 00:48:33,444
Legwork today.

1315
00:48:33,511 --> 00:48:35,646
- Building owners tomorrow!
- Building owners tomorrow!

1316
00:48:37,047 --> 00:48:38,249
Forget it! You already have someone!

1317
00:48:41,385 --> 00:48:42,219
What?

1318
00:48:42,286 --> 00:48:43,554
It can't be me.

1319
00:48:45,222 --> 00:48:48,692
Even if you lack something as an actor...

1320
00:48:48,759 --> 00:48:51,829
The others were dozing off or daydreaming
during your lecture.

1321
00:48:51,896 --> 00:48:53,631
You're starting to sound like a con man!

1322
00:48:53,697 --> 00:48:57,234
I could make an estimate
based on what your parents have.

1323
00:48:57,301 --> 00:49:00,137
CHICKEN SISTERS
<i>I could offer it at a lower fee if needed.</i>
